<L>__{interior bus day}
<A>__{... walter rides, head back, eyes closed. the bus comes to a stop and a couple of passengers get on. walter opens his eyes. the girl with binoculars comes to sit in the seat ahead of walter. walter stares at the girl. the bus pulls up to another stop it is walter's. the doors to the bus open. walter looks at the doors, he does not move. the doors close. he looks back at the girl. the bus drives on.}
